com.jaalee.sdk

Class Beacon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jaalee.sdk.Beacon

  • public class Beacon
extends java.lang.Object
    Immutable representations of single beacon. Two beacons are considered equal if their proximity UUID, major and minor are equal. This mimics CLBeacon from iOS.
